<li id="cite_note-uwe.ac.uk_RR645_1.5_Findings-19">^ <a href="#cite_ref-uwe.ac.uk_RR645_1.5_Findings_19-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-uwe.ac.uk_RR645_1.5_Findings_19-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-uwe.ac.uk_RR645_1.5_Findings_19-2" title=""><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-uwe.ac.uk_RR645_1.5_Findings_19-3" title=""><sup><i><b>d</b></i></sup></a> Woods, Ashley and Woods, <a href="http://www.dfes.gov.uk/research/data/uploadfiles/RR645.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.dfes.gov.uk/research/data/uploadfiles/RR645.pdf" rel="nofollow"><i>Steiner Schools in England</i>, University of West of England, Bristol: Research Report RR645</a>, section 1.5, "Findings from the survey and case studies"</li>
