<li>Aeppli, W., <i>The Developing Child</i> Anthroposophic Press <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0880104910" class="internal">ISBN 0-88010-491-0</a></li>
<li>Clouder, C. and Rawson, M., <i>Waldorf Education</i> Floris Books <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0863153968" class="internal">ISBN 0-86315-396-8</a></li>
<li>Cusick, L, <i>Waldorf Parenting Handbook</i> Mercury Press <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0916786757" class="internal">ISBN 0-916786-75-7</a></li>
<li>Edmunds, Francis, <i>An Introduction to Steiner Education</i> Rudolf Steiner Press <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/185584172X" class="internal">ISBN 1-85584-172-X</a></li>
