<p><a name="Waldorf_resources" id="Waldorf_resources"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Waldorf_education&amp;action=edit&amp;section=31" title="Edit section: Waldorf resources">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Waldorf resources</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.waldorflibrary.org/" class="external text" title="http://www.waldorflibrary.org/" rel="nofollow">Online Waldorf Library</a></li>
<li>Research journals
<ul>
<li><i>Paideia</i>, the journal of the Steiner-Waldorf Schools Fellowship in Britain.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.waldorflibrary.org/ResearchBulletin.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.waldorflibrary.org/ResearchBulletin.htm" rel="nofollow"><i>Research Bulletin</i> of the <i>Association of Waldorf Schools of North America</i></a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.waldorfresearchinstitute.org/" class="external text" title="http://www.waldorfresearchinstitute.org/" rel="nofollow">Waldorf Research Institute</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.siriusonline.de/verlag/zeitschriften.nsf/WebselectionFreiesGeistesleben?OpenForm" class="external text" title="http://www.siriusonline.de/verlag/zeitschriften.nsf/WebselectionFreiesGeistesleben?OpenForm" rel="nofollow"><i>Erziehungskunst</i></a>, the organ of the German Association of Waldorf Schools</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><a href="http://www.dieWaldorfs.waldorf.net/list.html" class="external text" title="http://www.dieWaldorfs.waldorf.net/list.html" rel="nofollow">The International List of Famous Waldorf Alumni (...and Waldorf Parents)</a></li>
</ul>
