<li><a href="http://www.plymouth.ac.uk/courses/undergraduate/0544/BA+(Hons)+Steiner+Waldorf+Education" class="external text" title="http://www.plymouth.ac.uk/courses/undergraduate/0544/BA+(Hons)+Steiner+Waldorf+Education" rel="nofollow">Plymouth University BA in Steiner/Waldorf Education</a></li>
